From 0d62d81496da03ced5cf4caac931a6d640dd2e67 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 7 Jun 2026 06:36:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Add test suite for pure-function modules and CI workflow

Introduces pytest infrastructure and 59 unit tests covering:
- moments.py: Gaussian moment orders 0/1/2, zero-distribution safety, error handling
- temperature_anisotropy.py: safe_ratio edge cases, temperature_profile scaling, region_averages
- energy_partition.py (OSIRIS): species/field energy profiles, partition_by_region
- flash_energy_partition.py: energy_densities (all channels, unit correctness), partition_by_region, partition_summary

Includes lightweight stubs for osh5def and analysis_utils so tests run
without the full OSIRIS/astropy stack. Adds pyproject.toml for pytest
config and a GitHub Actions workflow to run tests on every push/PR.

